README
Generalized R script to calculate ASE with data and list of gene names/IDs.
Scripts are modified from Esfeld, Berardi, Moser et al. 2018. Originally written by M. Moser, modified by AB.
  See https://github.com/Kuhlemeier-lab/Pseudogenization_and_resurrection_CB for original scripts and further examples.
  
Data file: F1s.strict.counts.short.sorted
List of flavonoid genes: petunia_flavonoid_pathway_gene_names_and_ids.txt
Analysis file: AX_EXS_st4_ASE_ax303_forpub.R

contact A. Berardi for questions: andrea.berardi (at) ips.unibe.ch or andreaberardi (at) fas.harvard.edu
